<div class="status-header">
    <div class="tag">Congratulations</div>
    <h1>Your Quote was Accepted!</h1>
    <p>Great news! Your quote for <strong>{{productName}}</strong> has been accepted by the buyer.</p>
</div>

<div class="highlight-box">
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Order Reference</div>
        <div class="info-value">Order #{{orderId}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Order Value</div>
        <div class="info-value">₹{{grandTotal}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; color: #2563eb;">Next Step: Waiting for Buyer to fund Escrow.</p>
</div>

<p>
    You will be notified as soon as the payment is secured in the BulkMandi Escrow account. You can track this order in your seller dashboard.
</p>

<p style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #ef4444; margin-top: 20px;">
    ⚠️ Please do not dispatch material until you receive the payment confirmation notification.
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
    <a href="{{orderUrl}}" class="btn">View Order Details</a>
</div>
